Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么早起床啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你到底打算做多少煎蛋卷啊…
